# Host-native shared library bundling marker
#
# The :mmkv:cmakeBuildDesktopMacos/Linux/WindowsShared Gradle task writes
# libmmkv-kmp.{dylib,so,dll} into processedResources/desktop/main/native/<os-arch>/
# before the JAR is assembled. This file just ensures the resources source
# directory is non-empty so Gradle's processResources task does not skip with
# NO-SOURCE, which would prevent our bundling doLast block from running.
